---
title: Teriyaki Popcorn Chicken & Cheesy Corn with Peanut Rice & Asian Radish Slaw
description: Asian cuisine isn’t shy about using big, bold and outrageous flavours. This sticky chicken is no exception. We've taken fried
chicken and have teamed it with cheesy corn over nutty rice and an apple salad for an absolutely vibrant feast.
